{"id":365157,"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/40/27/402777.jpg","floor":"#1","group":"班固米做菜人","groupHref":"/group/zuocai","groupThumb":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/icon/m/000/00/43/4324.jpg?r=1574965416","message":"来国外一个多月，人愈发懒惰，明明说好要多自炊，可最后还是图方便去了<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">  刚好今日秋高气爽，阳光明媚，趁远离冰冷的屏幕和房间亲近大自然的机会，绕道去中超买点食材做点菜吃。<br><br>看到中超的豆腐不错，又顺手买了一瓶郫县豆瓣酱，那就做份家常豆腐吧。<br><br>豆腐切块，锅里油烧到三成热，下豆腐开煎：<br><a href=\"https://imgtu.com/i/4yJf1I\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener noreferrer\" class=\"l\"><img src=\"https://z3.ax1x.com/2021/09/26/4yJf1I.jpg\" class=\"code\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" alt></a><br><br>豆腐一面微黄后翻面，煎到两面一样颜色：<br><a href=\"https://imgtu.com/i/4yJ4jP\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener noreferrer\" class=\"l\"><img src=\"https://z3.ax1x.com/2021/09/26/4yJ4jP.jpg\" class=\"code\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" alt></a><br><br>把两面煎好的豆腐捞出装盘放在一边：<br><a href=\"https://imgtu.com/i/4yJInf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener noreferrer\" class=\"l\"><img src=\"https://z3.ax1x.com/2021/09/26/4yJInf.jpg\" class=\"code\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" alt></a><br><br>锅里油留一半，大火烧到微微冒烟，下豆瓣酱炒匀：<br><a href=\"https://imgtu.com/i/4yJoB8\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener noreferrer\" class=\"l\"><img src=\"https://z3.ax1x.com/2021/09/26/4yJoB8.jpg\" class=\"code\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" alt></a><br><br>下煎好的豆腐，加水，转小火焖煮一会儿（记得盖盖儿）：<br><a href=\"https://imgtu.com/i/4yJHAg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener noreferrer\" class=\"l\"><img src=\"https://z3.ax1x.com/2021/09/26/4yJHAg.jpg\" class=\"code\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" alt></a><br><br>煮五到十分钟，关火，撒一点白胡椒，淋少许锅边醋：<br><a href=\"https://imgtu.com/i/4yJO9s\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener noreferrer\" class=\"l\"><img src=\"https://z3.ax1x.com/2021/09/26/4yJO9s.jpg\" class=\"code\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" alt></a><br><br>装盘：<br><a href=\"https://imgtu.com/i/4yYGvt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener noreferrer\" class=\"l\"><img src=\"https://z3.ax1x.com/2021/09/26/4yYGvt.jpg\" class=\"code\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" alt></a><br>豆瓣酱的香气掺着一点醋香，很是下饭，豆腐外酥里嫩，吸了汤汁，一口吃一块，很满足。美中不足之处是忘买糖了，否则出锅时加一点提鲜，味道会更平衡。 ","time":"2021-9-26 05:33","title":"极简版家常豆腐","userId":"402777","userName":"Clippers","userSign":""}